  <brief_title>Incisional Hernia After Midline Versus Transverse Extraction Incision in Laparoscopic Colectomy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Incisional Hernia After Midline Versus Transverse Extraction Incision in Laparoscopic Colectomy: A Pilot Randomized Trial</official_title>
